```

This is the full contents of the `up.sql` in question. Here's some parts of the code:

```rs
mod sqlite {
    #[derive(EmbedMigrations)]
    #[embed_migrations_options(migrations_path = "migrations/sqlite")]
    struct _Dummy;
}
...
sqlite::run_with_output(conn, out) // fails
```
